dc_description_s: Popluation of Placer County California and surrounding areas. This dataset contains Census counts from 2000 and 2010. It also conatins estimated 2016 population (Source: ESRI, 2016) and population projections for 2021 (source: ESRI, 2016). This dataset is aggregated to the cenusus tract level. Placer County Geographic Information Systems. (2016). Population, Placer County, California, 2016. Placer County Geographic Information Systems. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/qp684sk2392 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
